*kopete-0.12_alpha1-r1 (05 Mar 2006)

  05 Mar 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/kopete-3.5.x-msn-filetransfer.patch, +kopete-0.12_alpha1-r1.ebuild:
  Add patch from upstream to fix MSN filetransfer bug.

  05 Mar 2006; Hanno Boeck <hanno@gentoo.org> kopete-0.12_alpha1.ebuild:
  Add ~x86 keyword.

  28 Feb 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/kopete-0.12_alpha1-xscreensaver.patch, kopete-0.12_alpha1.ebuild:
  Add patch to disable xscreensaver and add a useflag to map it with. Also fix
  modular x dependencies.

*kopete-0.12_alpha1 (21 Feb 2006)

  21 Feb 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +kopete-0.12_alpha1.ebuild:
  Add kopete 0.12_alpha1, released outside KDE's release cycle. Masked as it's
  still an alpha release; blocks kde-base/kopete.

